---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"
    />
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
  </Fragment>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <header class="top-nav">
      <a class="top-nav__brand" href="#top">Huangshan Stay Guide</a>
      <details class="city-switcher">
        <summary>城市：黄山</summary>
        <div class="city-switcher__menu">
          <a href="/">哈尔滨</a>
          <a href="/huangshan">黄山</a>
        </div>
      </details>
      <nav class="top-nav__links" aria-label="页面导航">
        <a href="#route">路线</a>
        <a href="#plan">三日游</a>
        <a href="#picks">景点</a>
        <a href="#gallery">相册</a>
        <a href="#notes">说明</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" id="top">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Huangshan Travel Guide</p>
        <h1>专属黄山旅游攻略</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          如果你准备第一次去黄山，最舒服的走法不是只冲一个山顶打卡，而是把“上山住一晚的主景线”和“山下的徽州古村、老街夜色”一起拼成一趟完整旅行。
        </p>
        <p class="lead lead-soft">
          这份版本默认你住在汤口镇附近，先把黄山主景观走顺，再把宏村、西递和屯溪一起接上，适合想拍云海、松石、古村和夜色的人。
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#route">先看地图路线</a>
          <a href="#plan">再看三日安排</a>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight-list">
          {quickFacts.map((item) => <span>{item}</span>)}
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-panel">
        <p class="panel-label">三日安排</p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <strong>Day 1</strong>
            <span>上山主景线：云谷索道、光明顶，晚上住山上。</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Day 2</strong>
            <span>精华延伸线：西海大峡谷、迎客松，下山后接宏村。</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Day 3</strong>
            <span>收尾慢逛线：西递、屯溪老街和黎阳 in 巷。</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-route" id="route">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p>点击地图钉切换</p>
        <h2>地图版路线总览</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="route-explorer">
        <div class="route-map">
          <div class="route-map__header">
            <div class="route-map__legend">
              <span><i class="route-map__legend-dot route-map__legend-dot--hotel"></i>酒店据点</span>
              <span><i class="route-map__legend-dot route-map__legend-dot--day1"></i>Day 1 上山主景</span>
              <span><i class="route-map__legend-dot route-map__legend-dot--day2"></i>Day 2 精华 + 宏村</span>
              <span><i class="route-map__legend-dot route-map__legend-dot--day3"></i>Day 3 古村 / 老街</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="route-map-canvas" class="route-map__canvas" aria-label="黄山与周边路线地图"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="route-panels">
          {routeDetailSpots.map((spot) => (
            <article
              class:list={["route-card", `route-card--${spot.id}`, spot.id === "yungu" && "is-active"]}
              data-route-card={spot.id}
            >
              <div class="route-card__head">
                <p>{spot.order} · {spot.time}</p>
                <h3>{spot.title}</h3>
                <span>{spot.day} · {spot.area}</span>
              </div>

              <p class="route-card__summary">{spot.summary}</p>

              <div class="route-card__content">
                <section>
                  <h4>历史与看点</h4>
                  <ul>
                    {spot.history.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
                  </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                  <h4>吃什么更顺路</h4>
                  <ul>
                    {spot.food.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
                  </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                  <h4>拍照点位</h4>
                  <ul>
                    {spot.photoSpots.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
                  </ul>
                </section>
              </div>

              {spot.photos.length > 0 ? (
                <div class="route-card__photos">
                  {spot.photos.map((photo) => (
                    <figure>
                      <button
                        type="button"
                        class="route-card__photo-button"
                        data-gallery-open
                        data-image={photo.image}
                        data-alt={photo.alt}
                        data-title={spot.title}
                        data-note={photo.caption}
                        aria-label={`查看${spot.title}大图`}
                      >
                        <img src={photo.image} alt={photo.alt} loading="lazy" />
                      </button>
                      <figcaption>{photo.caption}</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                  ))}
                </div>
              ) : (
                <div class="route-card__empty">
                  这站先放完整攻略信息，后续如果你补拍了实景照片，也可以继续加进来。
                </div>
              )}
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-days" id="plan">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p>按天安排行程</p>
        <h2>黄山三日游版本</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="days-grid">
        {tripDays.map((day) => (
          <article class="day-card">
            <div class="day-card__head">
              <p>{day.day}</p>
              <h3>{day.title}</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="day-card__subtitle">{day.subtitle}</p>
            <ul class="day-card__schedule">
              {day.schedule.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
            </ul>
            <p class="day-card__meta"><strong>推荐美食：</strong>{day.recommendedFood.replace("推荐美食：", "")}</p>
            <p class="day-card__meta"><strong>不能食用：</strong>{day.avoidFood.replace("不能食用：", "")}</p>
            <p class="day-card__meta"><strong>交通建议：</strong>{day.traffic}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-picks" id="picks">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p>按喜好换玩法</p>
        <h2>黄山与周边著名景点参考</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="picks-grid">
        {nearbyPicks.map((spot) => (
          <article class="pick-card">
            <button
              type="button"
              class="pick-card__image-button"
              data-gallery-open
              data-image={spot.image}
              data-alt={spot.alt}
              data-title={spot.title}
              data-note={spot.detail}
              aria-label={`查看${spot.title}大图`}
            >
              <img class="pick-card__image" src={spot.image} alt={spot.alt} loading="lazy" />
            </button>
            <p class="pick-card__tag">{spot.tag}</p>
            <h3>{spot.title}</h3>
            <p class="pick-card__detail">{spot.detail}</p>
            <p class="pick-card__tip">{spot.tip}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="gallery">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>完整相册</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-carousel" data-gallery-carousel>
        <p class="gallery-carousel__hint">左右滑动查看，点击图片可放大。</p>

        <div class="gallery-carousel__viewport" data-gallery-viewport>
          {gallery.map((item) => (
            <figure class="gallery-slide">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="gallery-slide__image-button"
                data-gallery-open
                data-image={item.image}
                data-alt={item.alt}
                data-title={item.title}
                data-note={item.note}
                aria-label={`查看${item.title}大图`}
              >
                <img src={item.image} alt={item.alt} loading="lazy" />
              </button>
              <figcaption>
                <strong>{item.title}</strong>
                <p>{item.note}</p>
              </figcaption>
            </figure>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-notes" id="notes">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p>最后补三句</p>
        <h2>这一条路线为什么值得照着走</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="notes-grid">
        <article class="note-card">
          <h3>住山上一晚更值</h3>
          <p>
            黄山最怕的不是景点少，而是时间切得太碎。把第一天做成上山主景线并住山上一晚，第二天的云海、峡谷和下山节奏都会轻松很多。
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="note-card">
          <h3>天气比路线更重要</h3>
          <p>
            黄山的体验和天气绑定得很深。遇到云海、薄雾、雨后放晴，整座山会完全不一样，所以第二天一定要给路线留一点收放空间。
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="note-card">
          <h3>古村是这趟旅行的另一半</h3>
          <p>
            如果只上山不下村，黄山这趟会更像一次体力挑战。把宏村、西递和屯溪老街接进来，旅行会从单纯看景变成更完整的徽州体验。
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>这份黄山攻略会持续更新，之后你补充新的山上天气、古村照片或替换路线，也可以继续沿着这套结构往里加。</p>
      <a href="#top">回到顶部</a>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <dialog class="gallery-lightbox" data-gallery-lightbox>
    <button type="button" class="gallery-lightbox__close" data-gallery-close aria-label="关闭大图">
      关闭
    </button>
    <div class="gallery-lightbox__content">
      <img src="" alt="" data-gallery-lightbox-image />
      <div class="gallery-lightbox__caption">
        <strong data-gallery-lightbox-title></strong>
        <p data-gallery-lightbox-note></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </dialog>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-shell {
    width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 108px 0 72px;
  }

  .top-nav {
    position: fixed;
